            <li>
                <a class="link" href="https://crm.org/articles/xerox-parc-and-the-origins-of-gui">Xerox PARC and the Origins of GUI</a>
                <p>A brief history of the fabled Silicon Valley research lab that invented the mouse, laser printer and graphical user interface.</p>
            </li>
			 <li>
                <a class="link" href="https://designreviewed.com/">Design Reviewed</a>
                <p>A pictorial history of printed graphic design articfacts, including book covers, magazines and brochures.</p>
            </li>
			<li>
                <a class="link" href="https://fontsinuse.com/uses/7902/byte-magazine-covers-1976-84">Byte Magazine covers, 1976-84</a>
