            </li>
			<li>
                <a class="link" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eternal_September">Eternal September Wikipedia</a>
                <p>The history of our website's namesake. When college kids would flood the nascent internet in the early 1990s.</p>
            </li>
			<li>
                <a class="link" href="https://medium.com/processing-foundation/a-modern-prometheus-59aed94abe85">A Modern Prometheus</a>
                <p>The history of Processing, the first computer language created specifically for artists and designers. Written by Processing's founders Casey Reas and Ben Fry.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <a class="link" href="https://www.computerhistory.org/timeline/computers/">Timeline of Computer History</a>
                <p>A pictoral timeline that allows you to scroll through the history of computers, AI, the web, software and more.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <a class="link" href="https://www.webdesignmuseum.org/">Web Design Museum</a>
